Introduction

Chahee is a South Korean singer under Different Company. She was a member of the girl group Melody Day. In 2017, she and fellow members Yeoeun and Yoomin, participated in KBS 2TV's idol rebooting show The Unit, and finished in 16th place. She made her solo debut on May 6, 2020 with her digital single "Puzzle".
